      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/saudi-dairy-firm-plans-growth-as-nation-seeks-food-self-reliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯最大的乳制品生产商正进军海鲜和红肉领域，以满足日益增长的需求，凸显出该国提高粮食自给自足的雄心。]]></description>
